Class VParticleString

java.lang.Object
  punktiert.physics.VParticleGroup
      punktiert.physics.VParticleString

public class VParticleString
extends VParticleGroup

Utility builder/grouping/management class to connect a set of particles into a physical string/thread.

based on Karsten Schmidt's: toxi.physics.ParticleString
